The executive search firm Korn/Ferry International has named a new management 
team for Southern California, including Robert S. Rollo as managing director 
and Caroline Nahas, Elliot Gordon and Peter Kelly as managing vice presidents. 
Korn/Ferry's three Southern California offices are in downtown Los Angeles, 
Century City and Orange County. 
