<TEXT>
<P>
Peter E. Lowe has been named executive vice president and chief financial 
officer of Mitsui Manufacturers Bank, Los Angeles. Lowe joins Mitsui 
Manufacturers after a more than 20-year career with Security Pacific, where he 
also was chief financial officer for several of its subsidiaries. Executive 
Vice President William J. LaBelle, whose position formerly encompassed the 
chief financial officer function, becomes chief administrative officer. 
</P>
