MINORITIES; HOST INTERNATIONAL INC; MINORITY OWNED BUSINESS; BUSINESS -- LOS 
ANGELES; JOINT VENTURES; CONTRACTS; LOS ANGELES DEPARTMENT OF AIRPORTS; 
BUSINESS ETHICS; CONSULTANTS; FEES 
</P>
