(MISSILE); ARMS CONTROL; MISSILES; POWELL, COLIN L; STRATEGIC ARMS REDUCTION 
TALKS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; CHENEY, RICHARD B; BUSH, 
GEORGE; UNITED STATES -- DEFENSE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
