<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The sentencing of John L. Molinaro and Donald P. Mangano Sr., convicted of more 
than 30 counts of bank fraud and conspiracy concerning now-defunct Ramona 
Savings &amp; Loan in Santa Ana, was delayed Monday and rescheduled for Feb. 13 
. . . Virgin Atlantic Airways announced that it is introducing completely 
nonsmoking flights between New York and London starting May 18. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
