</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA020790-0110 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 172902 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 7, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 2; Column 3; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
