<P>
Hallmark to Buy Back Network Debt: Hallmark Cards Inc. began an offer to buy 
back at a discount some $270 million in debt securities used to finance 
Univision Holdings Inc. under a plan to ease the debt burden on the 
unprofitable Spanish-language broadcaster. 
