</P>
<P>
Medfly hearing -- A comment that people made ill by malathion spraying should 
move out of the area was made Tuesday by Supervisor Thomas F. Riley and not by 
Supervisor Don R. Roth. Dianne Klein's column Wednesday inadvertently indicated 
that both made the suggestion. 
</P>
