APPOINTMENTS; APOLOGIES; ROBERTI, DAVID A; LANSDALE, MARIANTHI; CALIFORNIA 
STATE UNIVERSITY BOARD OF TRUSTEES; CALIFORNIA -- EDUCATION; LEGISLATION -- 
CALIFORNIA 
