Times; Photo, Mission Viejo's Jennifer Rohrig, top right, MARK BOSTER / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, Loara's Traci Titus, center,; Photo, and Ocean View's 
Jennifer Sullivan are some of the county's best big girls. JOHN FUNG / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, COLOR, CENTER STAGE Jennifer Sullivan of Ocean View, 
